o%20put%20Bard%20Extensions%20to%20the%20test%20on%20my%20own%20Gmail%2C%20to%20book%20a%20flight%2C%20and%20on%20Google%20search.%20Here's%20how%20the%20experience%20went.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOnce%20you've%20logged%20into%20your%20Google%20Account%20you'll%20see%20a%20window%20like%20this%20when%20you%20open%20up%20Bard.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222368%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bard%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6510569be2c0220019ef31a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221184%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EScreenshot%20from%20Bard%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%20reported%20that%20Bard%20Extensions%20is%20only%20available%20on%20personal%20accounts%20right%20now.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESince%20Bard%20is%20probably%20best%20for%20summarizing%20and%20retrieving%20information%20right%20now%2C%20I%20asked%20it%20do%20exactly%20that%20%E2%80%94%20retrieve%20the%20last%20two%20emails%20that%20my%20mom%20sent%20me.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221848%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bard%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651056d7e4e6ee001901be65%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22923%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EScreenshot%20from%20Google%20Bard%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20initial%20query%20I%20asked%20Bard%20to%20retrieve%20emails%20from%20a%20sender%20named%20'Padmini%20Varanasi'%20without%20specifying%20that%20she%20was%20my%20mom.%20So%2C%20I%20was%20pretty%20impressed%20to%20see%20that%20Bard%20had%20somehow%20strung%20together%20a%20few%20details%20to%20figure%20out%20that%20Padmini%20Varanasi%20was%2C%20indeed%2C%20my%20mom.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20email%20summaries%20were%20pretty%20good%20too%2C%20especially%20since%20I%20hadn't%20actually%20read%2C%20or%20even%20opened%20her%20emails%20to%20me.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMy%20second%20order%20of%20business%20was%20to%20see%20if%20Bard%20could%20draft%20a%20response%20%E2%80%94%20this%20is%20where%20Roose%20said%20it%20might%20struggle.%20I%20decided%20to%20keep%20my%20request%20simple%2C%20without%20specifying%20a%20tone%20of%20voice%2C%20to%20see%20what%20it%20might%20come%20up%20with.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221728%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bard%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65105837e2c0220019ef31db%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22864%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EScreenshot%20from%20Google%20Bard%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20helpful%20that%20Bard%20had%20already%20given%20me%20summaries%20of%20two%20emails%20that%20my%20mom%20had%20sent%20me.%20I%20used%20that%20to%20ask%20it%20to%20draft%20a%20response%20about%20Lenovo's%20Global%20CIO.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EBard's%20response%20would%20have%20been%20pretty%20solid%20if%20this%20was%20drafted%20in%20a%20professional%20context.%20On%20a%20personal%20level%2C%20though%2C%20it%20was%20way%20too%20formal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ended%20up%20showing%20it%20to%20my%20mom%2C%20and%20she%20actually%20laughed%20out%20loud.%20She%20said%20she'd%20probably%20also%20be%20concerned%20if%20she%20ever%20received%20an%20email%20from%20me%20officially%20thanking%20her%20for%20forwarding%20me%20something%2C%20and%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3Ban%20interesting%20and%20timely%20read.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ESigning%20off%20the%20email%20with%20%26quot%3Blove%26quot%3B%20was%20a%20nice%20touch%2C%20though%2C%20and%20definitely%20something%20I'd%20do%20if%20I%20ever%20needed%20to%20email%20my%20mom%20about%20anything%20%E2%80%94%20generative%20AI%2C%20Lenovo%2C%20and%20all.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20wanted%20to%20see%20whether%20I%20could%20really%20implement%20Bard%20into%20my%20daily%20work%20flow.%20One%20of%20my%20tasks%20at%20work%20every%20morning%20is%20to%20scan%20the%20news%20of%20the%20day%20and%20pitch%20ideas%20for%20a%20quick%20story.%20I%20usually%20look%20through%20the%20newsletters%20I%20receive%20to%20pitch%20ideas%2C%20so%20I%20decided%20to%20put%20Bard%20up%20to%20the%20same%20task.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221878%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bard%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65105ec9e2c0220019ef3220%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22939%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EScreenshot%20from%20Google%20Bard%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20liked%20that%20Bard%20focused%20on%20timely%20themes%20of%20generative%20AI%2C%20Gen%20Z%2C%20and%20consumer%20habits%2C%20my%20instinct%20was%20that%20this%20would%20probably%20be%20rejected%20for%20being%20too%20broad.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EMy%20editor%20that%20day%20also%20agreed%20the%20angle%20was%20too%20vague%2C%20and%20said%20while%20it's%20certainly%20a%20timely%20and%20relevant%20topic%2C%20it's%20not%20very%20original.%20Insider%20has%20already%20published%20multiple%20stories%20in%20recent%20months%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ai-can-help-gen-z-succeed-workplace-2023-7%5C%22%3Einterviewing%20Gen%20Zers%20and%20experts%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-zer-uses-ai-create-content-2023-7%5C%22%3Egenerative%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20asked%20it%20to%20give%20me%20a%20few%20more%20specific%20suggestions.%20Here's%20what%20it%20came%20up%20with.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221810%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bard%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651064b5e4e6ee001901befb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22905%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EScreenshot%20from%20Google%20Bard%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20ideas%20definitely%20seemed%20a%20little%20more%20focused%2C%20my%20feeling%20was%20that%20they%20were%20still%20pretty%20general%2C%20and%20honestly%2C%20not%20that%20revelatory%20to%20make%20it%20into%20an%20actual%20story.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThat%20said%2C%20the%20first%20idea%20%E2%80%94%20How%20Gen%20Z%20consumers%20are%20using%20generative%20Al%20to%20create%20their%20own%20personalized%20fashion%20designs%20%E2%80%94%20did%20provide%20an%20interesting%20starting%20point%20for%20research.%20I%20think%20it%20would%20be%20fun%2C%20as%20Bard%20suggested%2C%20to%20find%20an%20actual%20Gen%20Zer%20who%20was%20making%20their%20own%20clothes%20with%20generative%20AI%20and%20interview%20them%20for%20a%20story.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20editor's%20feedback%20was%20that%20these%20were%20slightly%20stronger%20than%20the%20original%20pitch%2C%20but%20ultimately%20not%20very%20newsworthy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20was%20curious%20to%20see%20how%20incisive%20Bard%20could%20be%20now%20that%20it%20had%20access%20to%20a%20wealth%20of%20information%20about%20me.%20So%2C%20I%20asked%20it%20to%20determine%20my%20%26quot%3Bgreatest%20flaw%26quot%3B%20based%20on%20my%20inbox.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221658%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22flaws%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65106076e2c0220019ef322f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22829%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EScreenshot%20from%20Bard%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20should%20caveat%20this%20by%20saying%20I%20was%20taking%20a%20page%20from%20Roose's%20playbook%20here.%20He%20mentioned%20on%20Hard%20Fork%20that%20when%20he%20asked%20Bard%20to%20analyze%20his%20Gmail%2C%20and%20tell%20him%20with%20%26quot%3Breasonable%20certainty%26quot%3B%20what%20his%20biggest%20psychological%20issues%20were%2C%20Bard%20said%20that%20he%20worried%20about%20the%20future.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EBard%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20told%20me%20that%20I%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bperfectionist%26quot%3B%20who%20may%20have%20%26quot%3Bhigh%20standards%20for%20myself%20and%20others%26quot%3B%20which%20sounded%20a%20bit%20like%20an%20answer%20I%20might%20give%20to%20a%20job%20interviewer%20who%20asked%20me%20to%20describe%20my%20biggest%20weakness.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EBard%20also%20suggested%20that%20I%20might%20be%20%26quot%3Ba%20workaholic%26quot%3B%20who%20is%20%26quot%3Bpassionate%26quot%3B%20about%20my%20work%2C%20but%20may%20be%20neglecting%20my%20relationships%20or%20health.%20%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIt%20also%20made%20sure%2C%20though%2C%20to%20include%20a%20note%20availing%20itself%20of%20any%20responsibility%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20may%20not%20have%20any%20of%20these%20flaws%2C%20or%20you%20may%20have%20other%20flaws%20that%20are%20not%20mentioned%20here.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EBased%20on%20this%2C%20I'd%20say%20that%20Bard%20has%20one%20clear%20flaw%20(or%20strength)%20depending%20on%20your%20perspective.%20It's%20good%20at%20flattering%20users%20while%20keeping%20its%20language%20evasive%2C%20which%2C%20perhaps%2C%20is%20as%20important%20a%20skill%20for%20an%20AI%20assistant%20as%20it%20is%20for%20any%20working%20professional.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMoving%20on%20from%20my%20inbox%2C%20I%20tested%20out%20Bard's%20flight%20booking%20capabilities%2C%20by%20providing%20potential%20dates%20for%20a%20trip%20to%20Paris%20that%20my%20friends%20had%20floated%20to%20me%20recently.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221274%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bard%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65106760e4e6ee001901bf2f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22955%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EScreenshot%20from%20Bard%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20asked%20Bard%20beforehand%20what%20websites%20it%20would%20use%20to%20find%20flights%2C%20it%20mentioned%20Kayak%2C%20Skyscanner%2C%20Expedia%2C%20and%20Momondo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20Bard%20gave%20me%20flight%20options%2C%20though%2C%20it%20didn't%20compare%20them%20across%20websites.%20(There%20are%20other%20websites%20that%20do%20this%20of%20course%2C%20but%20they%20usually%20open%20up%20a%20ton%20of%20browser%20pages%20too).%20Bard%20only%20seemed%20to%20pull%20from%20Google%20Flights%20which%20is%20where%20I%20usually%20look%20for%20flights%20anyways.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELater%2C%20while%20working%2C%20I%20ended%20up%20having%20to%20Google%20myself%2C%20and%20since%20I%20had%20enabled%20Bard%20Extensions%2C%20a%20window%20immediately%20popped%20up%20with%20a%20small%20biography%20of%20me.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22812%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bard%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65105277e2c0220019ef3133%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221172%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EScreenshot%20of%20Bard%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20biography%2C%20however%2C%20filled%20with%20a%20litany%20of%20embellishments%20and%20full%20on%20fabrications.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Bard%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20was%20born%20in%20India.%20%3Cem%3EI%20was%20actually%20born%20in%20Wisconsin%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI'm%20fluent%20in%20English%20and%20Hindi.%20%3Cem%3EI%20took%20a%20few%20Hindi%20classes%20in%20college%2C%20but%20I'm%20definitely%20not%20fluent%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI'm%20a%20member%20of%20the%20National%20Association%20of%20Black%20Journalists%20and%20the%20Asian%20American%20Journalists%20Association.%20%3Cem%3EI'm%20not%20a%20member%20of%20either%20of%20these%20organizations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI'm%20a%20recipient%20of%20the%20Livingston%20Award%20for%20Young%20Journalists.%20%3Cem%3EThis%20would%20be%20great%2C%20but%20it's%20definitely%20not%20true%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20Bard%20painted%20a%20pretty%20glowing%20portrait%20of%20me%2C%20even%20referring%20to%20me%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Brising%20star%26quot%3B%20in%20one%20instance%2C%20but%20I'd%20say%20it's%20just%20further%20evidence%20that%20the%20tool%20is%20better%20with%20flattery%20than%20it%20is%20with%20facts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20nice%20thing%20about%20Bard's%20update%20is%20that%20it%20does%20have%20a%20button%20that%20users%20can%20press%20to%20%26quot%3Bfact-check%26quot%3B%20Bard's%20responses%20via%20Google%20Search.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221632%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bard%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65107cdce4e6ee001901c004%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22564%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EScreenshot%20of%20Google%20Bard%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20I%20asked%20Bard%20%26quot%3Bhow%20many%20parameters%20are%20there%20in%20GPT-4.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20hit%20that%20small%20%26quot%3BG%26quot%3B%20button%20Bard%20will%20fact-check%20its%20response%20via%20Google%20Search%20and%20highlight%20lines%20in%20green.%20In%20this%20case%2C%20if%20you%20click%20on%20the%20%26quot%3B1.76%20trillion%26quot%3B%20it%20will%20take%20you%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthe-decoder.com%2Fgpt-4-has-a-trillion-parameters%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estory%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20The%20Decoder%2C%20which%20is%20also%20one%20of%20the%20first%20results%20if%20you%20search%20the%20same%20question%20on%20Google.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESo%2C%20I%20went%20back%20to%20see%20if%20I%20could%20fact-check%20my%20own%20biography%20by%20typing%20%26quot%3Bwho%20is%20Lakshmi%20Varanasi%26quot%3B%20into%20Bard%20(with%20the%20expectation%20that%20it%20might%20also%20generate%20something%20entirely%20new).%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Google%20Bard%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6510755ce2c0220019ef332c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22242%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EScreenshot%20of%20Google%20Bard%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20presented%20me%20with%20a%20single%20line%20of%20Hindi%20transliterated%20into%20English%2C%20%26quot%3BMa