er%20during%20their%20ride%20over%20misinformation%20on%20the%20destination%20and%20assuming%20she%20was%20of%20Indian%20origin.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20said%2C%20'You%20are%20Indian%2C%20you%20are%20stupid'%2C%26quot%3B%2046-year-old%20Eurasian%20origin%20Janelle%20Hoeden%20said%20of%20the%20cab%20driver%20abuse%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20was%20with%20her%20nine-year-old%20daughter%20on%20the%20ride%2C%20The%20Straits%20Times%20reported%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHoeden%20recorded%20on%20her%20phone%20the%20interaction%20which%20got%20progressively%20more%20heated.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20had%20booked%20a%20ride%20on%20the%20ride-hailing%20platform%2C%20TADA%2C%20at%20around%202%20pm%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHoeden%20said%20the%20ride%20started%20uneventfully%20and%20she%20was%20talking%20to%20her%20child%20when%20suddenly%20the%20driver%20got%20upset%20that%20part%20of%20the%20road%20was%20blocked%20due%20to%20construction%20of%20an%20upcoming%20metro%2C%20MRT%20line%2C%20along%20the%20ride%20in%20Pasir%20Ris%20housing%20estate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20started%20shouting%20at%20me%2C%20saying%20that%20I%20gave%20him%20the%20wrong%20address%20and%20wrong%20directions%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%20--%20uploaded%20on%20her%20Facebook%20page%20and%20an%20account%20by%20a%20TikTok%20user%2C%20and%20later%20shared%20by%20alternative%20news%20site%20Wake%20Up%20Singapore%20--%20the%20driver%2C%20a%20Chinese%20man%2C%20is%20seen%20accusing%20Hoeden's%20daughter%20of%20being%20less%20than%201.35%20metres%20tall.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20repeatedly%20said%20her%20daughter%20was%20under%201.35%20metres%2C%20and%20Hoeden%20could%20be%20heard%20replying%20that%20the%20child%20was%201.37%20metres.%20He%20then%20called%20the%20girl%20%26quot%3Bvery%20illegal%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20believed%20the%20height%20is%20for%20the%20safety%20of%20passengers%20requiring%20child%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Land%20Transport%20Authority%20(LTA)%20states%20on%20its%20website%20that%20for%20safety%20reasons%2C%20all%20vehicles%20in%20Singapore%20must%20have%20booster%20seats%20or%20child%20restraints%20for%20passengers%20under%201.35%20metres%20in%20height.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20driver%20shouted%20at%20the%20woman%20while%20driving%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20are%20India(n)%2C%20I'm%20Chinese...%20You%20are%20the%20very%20worst%20kind...%26quot%3B%20Hoeden%20corrected%20the%20driver%2C%20saying%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20Singapore%20Eurasian%2C%20not%20Indian.%26quot%3B%20Eurasians%20are%20usually%20tanned%20and%20at%20times%20appear%20to%20be%20Indian%20in%20appearance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20he%20was%20verbally%20abusive%2C%20I%20was%20afraid%20that%20he%20would%20start%20getting%20physical%20with%20me%2C%20so%20I%20told%20her%20to%20record%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Singapore%20broadsheet%20quoted%20Hoeden%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhether%20I%20was%20tanned%20skin%2C%20or%20Indian%2C%20or%20otherwise%2C%20it's%20unacceptable%20what%20he%20said%20-%20it%20was%20totally%20uncalled%20for%2C%20that%20he%20pulled%20out%20the%20race%20card%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHer%20child%20was%20also%20shaken%20after%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20comments%20on%20'Wake%20Up%20Singapore's%20Instagram'%20post%20that%20highlighted%20the%20incident%2C%20Tada%20Singapore%20said%20it%20was%20investigating%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20Tada%2C%20we%20do%20not%20tolerate%20racism%2C%20discrimination%2C%20or%20abuse.%20Our%20team%20is%20investigating%20this%20issue.%20Thanks%20to%20everyone%20who%20brought%20this%20to%20our%20attention%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20comment%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Straits%20Times%20also%20had%20a%20Tada%20spokeswoman%20saying%20that%20the%20firm%20was%20aware%20of%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BRemarks%20or%20comments%20that%20i