%20The%20wedding%20ceremony%20was%20held%20at%20the%20Leela%20Palace.%20The%20duo%20is%20yet%20to%20make%20an%20official%20announcement%20on%20social%20media.%20If%20sources%20are%20to%20be%20believed%2C%20bride%20Parineeti%20Chopra%20wore%20a%20wedding%20outfit%20designed%20by%20ace%20designer%20Manish%20Malhotra.%20Fans%20are%20eagerly%20waiting%20to%20see%20the%20first%20glimpse%20of%20Raghav%20and%20Parineeti%20as%20Mr%20and%20Mrs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20captured%20by%20ANI%2C%20%3Ci%3Ebidai%20%3C%2Fi%3Esong%20%3Ci%3EKabira%3C%2Fi%3E%20from%20%3Ci%3EYeh%20Jawaani%20Hai%20Deewani%3C%2Fi%3E%20can%20be%20heard%20playing%20at%20the%20wedding%20venue%20while%20marriage%20rituals%20are%20being%20performed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20afternoon%2C%20the%20baraatis%20arrived%20on%20a%20boat%20adorned%20with%20decorations%20that%20showcased%20glimpses%20of%20Mewar%20tradition.%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20and%20Punjab%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20were%20spotted%20making%20their%20way%20to%20the%20wedding%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETennis%20star%20Sania%20Mirza%2C%20former%20cricketer%20Harbhajan%20Singh%2C%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%2C%20Shiva%20Sena%20leader%20Aditya%20Thackeray%2C%20and%20Manish%20Malhotra%20also%20marked%20their%20presence%20at%20the%20starry%20wedding.%20Parineeti's%20cousin%20and%20global%20star%20Priyanka%20Chopra%20gave%20Parineeti%20and%20Raghav's%20wedding%20a%20miss.%20However%2C%20Priyanka's%20mom%20Madhu%20Chopra%20attended%20the%20wedding.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20recently%20gave%20a%20hint%20that%20she%20might%20not%20be%20able%20to%20attend%20Parineeti's%20wedding%20to%20Raghav.%20Taking%20to%20Instagram%20on%20Saturday%2C%20she%20posted%20a%20happy%20picture%20of%20Parineeti.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20hope%20your%20happiness%20on%20your%20special%20day%20matches%20the%20joy%20in%20this%20picture%2C%20my%20dear%20cousin%2C%20Always%20sending%20you%20loads%20of%20love.%20%23newbeginnings%20%40parineetichopra%20%40raghavchadha88.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20D-day%2C%20Parineeti%20and%20Raghav%20held%20a%20sangeet%20in%20Udaipur%20with%20a%2090s%20theme.%20Punjabi%20singer%20Navraj%20Hans%20performed%20at%20the%20function.%20Reportedly%2C%20guests%20received%20cassettes%20with%20customized%20messages%20for%20them.%20The%20couple%20showcased%20their%20distinctive%20personal%20style%20on%20the%20auspicious%20occasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERaghav%20opted%20for%20a%20black%20indo-western%20ethnic%20outfit%2C%20while%20Parineeti%20sported%20a%20shimmering%20embroidered%20outfit%20with%20a%20beaded%20cape%20layered%20over%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBefore%20arriving%20in%20Udaipur%20for%20the%20main%20wedding%20festivities%2C%20Parineeti%20and%20Raghav%20hosted%20a%20sufi%20night%20for%20close%20friends%20and%20family%20members%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20got%20engaged%20on%20May%2013%20in%20Delhi.%20The%20star-studded%20ceremony%20was%20attended%20by%20several%20politicians%20including%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20Punjab%20CM%20Bhagwant%20Mann%2C%20former%20finance%20minister%20P%20Chidambaram%2C%20and%20Shiv%20Sena%20leader%20Aaditya%20Thackeray.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EParineeti%20and%20Raghav%20reportedly%20knew%20each%20other%20for%20several%20years%20before%20they%20began%20dating.%20The%20love%20story%20of%20Raghav-Parineeti%20might%20have%20blossomed%20in%20London%20as%20reportedly%20the%20duo%20studied%20together%20in%20a%20college%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20on%20the%20work%20front%2C%20Parineeti%20will%20share%20screen%20space%20with%20Diljit%20Dosanjh%20in%20Chamkila.%20Helmed%20by%20Imtiaz%20Ali%2C%20the%20film%20revolves%20around%20two%20famous%20Punjabi%20singers%20Amarjot%20Kaur%20and%20Amar%20Singh%20Chamkila.%20She%20also%20has%20Mission%20Raniganj%3A%20The%20Great%20Bharat%20Rescue%20along%20with%20Akshay%20Kumar%20in%20her%20kitty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%