5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAmar%20Ujala%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20BJP%20treated%20entrants%20from%20other%20parties%20as%20%E2%80%9Cuntouchables%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20made%20a%20member%20of%20the%20state%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20working%20committee%20but%20resigned%20recently%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fmadhya-pradesh%2Fscindia-associate-pramod-tandon-who-joined-bjp-with-him-returns-to-congress-2698574%5C%22%3EPTI%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20was%20said%20to%20be%20a%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%20loyalist.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPTI%20also%20reported%20that%20Samandar%20Patel%2C%20another%20BJP%20working%20committee%20member%20who%20joined%20the%20Congress%20recently%2C%20said%20that%20Tandon%20was%20the%20sixth%20person%20from%20the%20Scindia%20%E2%80%98camp%E2%80%99%20to%20have%20re-joined%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERamkishore%20Shukla%20and%20Dinesh%20Malhar%20have%20been%20part%20of%20the%20BJP%20for%20a%20longer%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bhaskar.com%2Flocal%2Fmp%2Findore%2Fmhow%2Fnews%2Fsenior-bjp-leader-ramkishore-shukla-will-join-congress-131883445.html%5C%22%3Etold%20Hindi%20newspaper%20%3Cem%3EDainik%20Bhaskar%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20BJP%20did%20not%20give%20opportunities%20to%20local%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMalhar%20said%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9CBJP%20is%20no%20longer%20the%20party%20that%20used%20to%20respect%20its%20workers%20who%20toiled%20to%20strengthen%20its%20base%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Findore%2Fbjps-dinesh-malhar-to-join-congress-today%2Farticleshow%2F103879536.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ethe%C2%A0%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20few%20months%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmadhya-pradesh-bjp-internal-rift-congress-edge-per