nservative%20Hindu%20family%20system%20where%20the%20man%20was%20the%20patriarch%20and%20the%20family%2C%20his%20property.%20Women%20were%20to%20be%20defined%20as%20mother%2C%20daughter%2C%20sister%20or%20%3Cem%3Ebhabi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(sister-in-law)%20and%20the%20patriarchs%20laid%20down%20the%20law%2C%20both%20within%20homes%20and%20outside.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20326px)%2085vw%2C%20326px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mrinal%20Pande%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22326%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783.jpg%20525w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783-246x300.jpg%20246w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-642789%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22397%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20was%20a%20simultaneous%20dilution%20of%20earlier%20government%20programmes%20like%20the%20MGNREGA%20and%20food%20subsidies%2C%20along%20with%20substantial%20changes%20in%20the%20admission%20policies%2C%20syllabi%20and%20faculties%20in%20institutes%20of%20learning.%20All%20this%20slowly%20eroded%20much%20of%20the%20free%20choices%20that%20had%20become%20available%20to%20the%20women%20and%20the%20marginalised%20courtesy%20various%20rights%20movements%2C%20progressive%20laws%20and%20judgments%20from%20the%20apex%20court.%20During%20and%20after%20COVID-19%2C%20this%20resulted%20in%20major%20losses%20for%20working%20women%20in%20all%20categories.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGiven%20this%20background%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwomens-reservation-bill-cabinet-clear-33-percent%5C%22%3Ethe%20law%20granting%2033%25%20reservation%20to%20women%20in%20the%20legislature%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20certainly%20a%20positive%20step.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20law%2C%20conceptually%2C%20is%20three%20decades%20old%20and%20began%20stirring%20when%2033%25%20seats%20were%20reserved%20for%20women%20in%20the%20Panchayati%20Raj%20system.%20The%20parties%20then%20in%20the%20opposition%20had%20declared%20it%20a%20non-starter%20but%20with%202024%20general%20elections%20looming%20large%20over%20the%20horizon%2C%20women%E2%80%99s%20vote%20bank%20has%20an%20undeniable%20power%20of%20deciding%20the%20fate%20of%20the%20next%20government.%20The%20same%20rightwing%20that%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fkarnataka-cm-siddaramaiah-slams-centre-on-blocks-to-implementing-women-reservation-bill-2439719-2023-09-24%5C%22%3Eplayed%20a%20role%20in%20blocking%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20Bill%3C%2Fa%3E%20then%20chose%20to%20rebrand%20it%20as%20Nari%20Shakti%20Vandan%20Adhiniyam%20%E2%80%93%20a%20most%20progressive%20step%20taken%20by%20the%20government%20in%20Amrit%20Kaal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%20voting%20on%20the%20Bill%2C%20all%20the%20well%20known%20female%20politician%20baiters%20within%20the%20legislative%20bodies%20and%20political%20parties%20thumped%20their%20tables%20in%20happy%20assent.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20those%20who%20had%20registered%20their%20displeasure%20against%2033%25%20reservation%20for%20women%20on%20grounds%20that%20so%20many%20strong%20wilful%20women%20would%20pose%20a%20threat%20to%20our%20men%20and%20their%20masculinity%20(%3Cem%3Epaurush%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Epurusharth%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20were%20made%20to%20eat%20their%20words.%20Like%20chastened%20school%20boys%20when%20the%20bell%20rang%20all%20of%20them%20voted%20for%20the%20Bill%20as%20ordered.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20fact%20remains%20that%20in%202024%20the%20powerful%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20leadership%20is%20pitted%20against%20two%20major%20female%20leaders%20%E2%80%93%20Sonia%20and%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20with%20their%20vociferous%20troops%20of%20younger%20ones%20like%20Mahua%20Moitra%2C%20Kakoli%20Ghosh%20Dastidar%2C%20and%20Supriya%20Shrinate%2C%20with%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20bringing%20up%20the%20rear.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20legal%20luminaries%20the%20new%20law%20is%20a%20positive%20step%2C%20but%20it%20can%20be%20implemented%20only%20after%20the%20Census%20(last%20held%20in%202011)%20and%20time%20consuming%20delimitation%20exercises%20are%20completed%20and%20their%20results%20calculated%20and%20announced%20formally.%20Then%20there%20is%20the%20question%20of%20the%20women%20in%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20communities.%20They%20want%20a%20quota%20within%20the%20new%20quota%20%E2%80%93%20same%20as%20their%20sisters%20from%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20communities%20do.%20So%20nobody%20can%20tell%20the%20nation%20when%20the%20complex%20and%20time%20consuming%20exercises%20will%20begin%20and%20end%2C%20and%20how%20exactly%20the%20women%20in%20the%20OBC%20category%20will%20be%20included.%20Women%20should%20thus%20expect%20no%20miracles%20this%20once%20in%20ticket%20distribution.%20It%20will%20most%20probably%20be%20the%20same%20old%2C%20same%20old%20with%20a%20few%20usual%20freebies%20like%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Flpg-price-cut-modis-rakhi-gift-ends-up-drawing-attention-to-inflation%5C%22%3E%20comparatively%20%E2%80%98cheaper%E2%80%99%20gas%20cylinders%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20grains%20thrown%20in.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20interesting%20point%20concerns%20the%20contrast%20between%20repeated%20finger-wagging%20criticism%20of%20the%20dynasts%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20a%20woman%E2%80%99s%20family%20will%20still%20be%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20first%20criteria%20for%20a%20woman%E2%80%99s%20selection%20as%20an%20electoral%20candidate.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBe%20it%20noted%20also%20how%20Bollywood%20actors%20storming%20in%20to%20fill%20the%20void%20created%20by%20feminists%20and%20liberals%20have%20been%20speaking%20into%20every%20available%20TV%20mic%20with%20gushing%20words%20of%20praise%20for%20the%20visionary%20new%20beginning%20for%20Nari%20Shakti%20or%20woman%20power.%20Their%20proximity%20to%20power%20might%20be%20an%20early%20indicator%20of%20which%20way%20the%20wind%20is%20blowing%20for%20the%20selection%20of%20woman%20candidates.%20For%20the%20time%20being%2C%20men%20remain%20the%20political%20gate-keepers%20in%20most%20parties.%20It%20is%20no%20secret%20that%20men%20of%20a%20certain%20age%20are%20likely%20to%20confess%20that%20women%20candidates%20in%20India%20are%20less%20likely%20to%20win%20unless%20backed%20by%20a%20powerful%20clan%20and%20community.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.knightlab.com%2Flibs%2Ftimeline3%2Flatest%2Fembed%2Findex.html%3Fsource%3D1601B6of0DDLcqevG_UcSmg9POp-SSf0RVP-fHv36Cyk%26font%3DDefault%26lang%3Den%26initial_zoom%3D2%26height%3D650%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22650%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20no%20denying%20that%20women%20in%20India%20have%20come%20a%20long%20way%20from%20our%20parliament%20of%201952.%20Then%2C%20out%20of%20the%20total%20499%20seats%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20a%20mere%C2%A0%2022%20(4.41%25%20of%20the%20total)%20were%20occupied%20by%20women%20and%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20also%2C%20they%20numbered%20a%20mere%207.31%25%20of%20the%20total.%20Their%20numbers%20in%20the%20last%20(16%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth)%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ELok%20Sabha%20rose%20to%2011.23%25%20of%20all%20(543)%20seats%20and%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20they%20were%2011.62%25%20of%20the%20total%20number.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20But%20they%20have%20a%20long%20way%20to%20go%20yet%20before%20they%20come%20anywhere%20near%20the%20present%20day%20number%20of%20women%20parliamentarians%20in%20some%20other%20developing%20countries.%20Even%20Rwanda%20(56.3%25)%20and%20our%20neighbouring%20Nepal%20(33.2%25)%20have%20higher%20figures.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESoon%20after%20the%20NDA%2C%20led%20by%20the%20rightwing%20BJP%2C%20came%20to%20power%20in%202014%2C%20an%20ebullient%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20assembled%20his%20most%20trusted%20brains%20from%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20think-tank%20to%20create%20an%20image%20of%20his%20government%20as%20a%20progressive%20force.%20Empowerment%20of%20women%20was%20showcased%20by%20giving%20charge%20of%20the%20ministries%20of%20human%20resource%20development%2C%20finance%2C%20external%20affairs%2C%20food%20processing%2C%20and%20Ganga%20cleaning%20to%20women%20MPs.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20for%20ordinary%20women%2C%20one%20of%20the%20key%20takeaways%20from%20the%20past%20five%20years%20of%20NDA%20rule%20has%20been%20that%20even%20powerful%20women%20within%20the%20ruling%20party%20may%20not%20get%20their%20due.%20Their%20frequent%20TV%20appearances%2C%20dazzling%20lives%20and%20participation%20in%20global%20dos%2C%20can%20barely%20hide%20a%20guaranteed%20obedience%20to%20the%20male%20leadership.%20Or%20else%2C%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fbackstory-media-wrestlers-protest-brij-bhushan-singh%5C%22%3Ewomen%20athletes%20were%20protesting%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20their%20abuse%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fsupreme-court-manipur-video-survivors-petition%5C%22%3Etribal%20women%20paraded%20and%20groped%20naked%20on%20streets%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20would%20not%20have%20remained%20silent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWomen%20storming%20into%20parliament%20alone%20can%20reveal%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20India%2C%20how%20much%20of%20the%20state%20as%20we%20saw%20and%20experienced%20was%20determined%20by%20dominant%20social%20relations%20and%20the%20operative%20laws%20and%20instruments%20of%20a%20male%20state.%20If%20a%20state%20is%20built%20on%20the%20relative%20powerlessness%20of%2050%25%20of%20its%20citizens%2C%20(only%20one-tenth%20of%20whom%20are%20represented%20in%20the%20lawmaking%20legislative%20bodies)%2C%20could%20it%20ever%20see%20how%20male%20power%20in%20India%20(even%20in%20Amrit%20Kaal)%20is%20synonymous%20with%20state%20power%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20things%20stand%20today%2C%20and%20will%20during%20the%202024%20elections%2C%20formally%2C%20the%20state%20remains%20male.%20It%20will%20legitimise%20itself%20by%20imposing%20its%20own%20view%20of%20society%20as%20rational%20and%20the%20only%20acceptable%20one.%20Since%20the%20fabled%20reservation%20is%20perhaps%20not%20going%20to%20become%20a%20reality%20in%20the%20lifetime%20of%20my%20generation%2C%20we%20shall%2C%20until%20we%20live%2C%20be%20seeing%20women%20groups%20clustered%20around%20a%20beaming%20male%20PM%2C%20like%20happy%20sheep.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20they%20finally%20do%2C%20women%20getting%2033%25%20reserved%20seats%20in%20parliament%20and%20assemblies%20will%20usher%20in%20a%20truly%20revolutionary%20scenario.%20Because%20as%20Thomas%20Kuhn%20wrote%2C%20true%20political%20revolutions%20will%20often%20change%20political%20institutes%20in%20ways%20that%20they%20themselves%20have%20prohibited.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMrinal%20Pande%20is%20a%20writer%20and%20veteran%20journalist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695553014000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F24162044%2FF6kk7dtXkAEhH2a-1.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fwomens-reservation-bill-parliament%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20are%20a%20number%20of%20reasons%20why%20despite%20the%20women's%20reservation%20Bill%20becoming%20an%20Act%2C%20women%20should%20expect%20no%20miracles%20in%202024%2C%20in%20ticket%20distribution.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%2