except%20that%20my%20use%20of%20the%20metaphor%20is%20widely%20(and%20wildly)%20different%20from%20the%20meaning%20the%20ruling%20party%20scions%C2%A0attach%20to%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20engine%20pulls%20fast%20forward%2C%20embracing%20every%20bit%20of%20the%20latest%20technology%20that%20science%20makes%20possible%2C%20all%20the%20way%20upto%20the%20south%20side%20of%20the%20moon%3B%20the%20other%20rushes%20the%20republic%20backward%20to%20the%20mythic%20glories%20of%20an%20ancient%20past%2C%20stamped%20most%20emphatically%20on%20the%20spot%20where%20the%20rover%20landed%20as%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-landing-site-called-shiv-shakti-how-are-points-on-moon-named-101693181455182.html%5C%22%3EShiv-Shakti%20Sthal%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPut%20succinctly%2C%20the%20two%20engines%20denote%20two%20engines%20of%20the%20ruling%20right-wing%20ideology%20which%2C%20even%20if%20seen%20to%20be%20slightly%20different%20in%20direction%2C%20crucially%2C%20complement%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20trajectory%20to%20a%20common%20thesis.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20during%20the%20crusades%2C%20the%20dominant%20ideological%20contour%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cnew%20age%20of%20ambition%E2%80%9D%20is%20to%20project%20material%20victories%20as%20the%20matching%20expression%20of%20the%20strengths%20of%20a%20new%20collective%C2%A0religious%20identity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%2C%20the%20message%20goes%2C%20we%20are%20conquering%20technologies%2C%20reaching%20the%20moon%E2%80%99s%20south%20pole%2C%20engaging%20start-ups%20of%20all%20kind%2C%20running%20ahead%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20economies%2C%20because%20we%20now%20know%20the%20power%20of%20being%20Hindus%2C%20after%20all.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20could%20have%20been%20a%20more%20abrasively%20gauche%20demonstration%20of%C2%A0%20this%20concatenation%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20current%20history%20than%20afforded%20by%20the%20right%20honourable%20MP%2C%20Ramesh%20Bidhuri%2C%20who%20thought%20nothing%20of%20damning%20a%20fellow%20elected%20member%20in%20crass%2C%20hate-filled%20religious%20epithets%2C%20as%20if%20to%20say%2C%20you%20may%20be%20an%20elected%20representative%20too%2C%20but%20you%20now%20live%20on%20the%20sufferance%20of%20the%20ruling%20Hindu.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20all%2C%20do%20recall%20what%20the%20honourable%20prime%20minister%20himself%20said%20when%20he%20first%20entered%20the%20portals%20of%20parliament%20in%202014%3A%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20have%20achieved%20independence%20after%201200%20years.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThus%20if%20one%20engine%20is%20meant%20to%20scale%20the%20furthest%20reaches%20of%20technological%20modernity%2C%20the%20other%20is%20programmed%20to%20a%20revanchist%20agenda%20calculated%20to%20assert%20the%20glories%20of%20a%20cultural%20and%20religious%20past%2C%20versus%20the%20%E2%80%98Left-Liberal%20interregnum%E2%80%99%2C%20one%20that%20I%20define%20as%20the%20freedom%20movement%20and%C2%A0the%20six%C2%A0decades%20of%20rationalism.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEgalitarian%20Democracy%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETherefore%2C%20the%C2%A0struggling%20republic%C2%A0%20squeaks%2C%20to%20retain%20a%20semblance%20of%20an%20egalitarian%20democracy%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9C%20new%20age%20of%20ambition%E2%80%9D%20requires%20an%20unbridled%20centre%20of%20authority%20that%20is%20derived%20from%20a%20revived%20religious%2Fcultural%20assertion%20rather%20than%20from%20just%20universal%20adult%20franchise%20(although%20the%20latter%20may%20be%20retained%20as%20a%20necessary%20nuisance%20till%20the%20crusade%20fully%20reaches%20its%20culmination).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EImagine%20for%20a%20moment%2C%20if%20what%20Ramesh%20Bidhuri%20has%20hurled%20at%20Danish%20Ali%20was%20hur