ards%20Muslims%20and%20Christians.%20He%20has%20also%20repeatedly%20posited%20the%20interests%20of%20Muslims%20against%20those%20of%20the%20Hindus.%20Who%20can%20forget%20his%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FdPYZh6JV3V%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHum%20paanch%20humare%20pachis%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20jibe%20against%20Muslims%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.outlookindia.com%2Fwebsite%2Fstory%2Fshould-we-run-relief-camps-open-child-producing-centres%2F217398%5C%22%3Einsinuating%20that%20the%20relief%20camps%20of%20Muslims%20were%20actually%20factories%20for%20producing%20terrorists%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20Modi%20has%20always%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20his%20politics%20is%20based%20on%20anti-Muslim%20hatred%20and%20has%20never%20tried%20to%20shed%20that%20image%20.%20He%20knows%20that%20he%20is%20loved%20by%20his%20folk%20for%20this%20very%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20direct%20relationship%20between%20anti-Muslim%20violence%20or%20hatred%20and%20incivility.%20Crudity%20and%20obscenity%20cannot%20be%20separated%20from%20it.%20It%20cannot%20be%20that%20you%20accept%20violence%20and%20killing%20of%20Muslims%20and%20turn%20your%20nose%20up%20at%20abuses%20against%20them.%20Abuses%20precede%20or%20accompany%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESlurs%20are%20literal%20expressions%20of%20hatred%20and%20violence.%20Dalits%20of%20India%20understand%20this%20well.%20The%20verbal%20abuser%20knows%20that%20the%20person%20being%20abused%20cannot%20answer%20back.%20Verbal%20abuse%20is%20an%20effective%20weapon%20to%20repeatedly%20humiliate%2C%20undermine%20and%20prove%20inferior.%20Jews%20would%20tell%20you%20that%20the%20Holocaust%20was%20a%20culmination%20of%20a%20long%20culture%20of%20expressions%20of%20anti-Jew%20hatred%20nurtured%20by%20the%20Nazis.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20done%20on%20the%20streets%2C%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fup-teacher-forces-fellow-students-to-slap-muslim-child-ncpcr-orders-not-to-circulate-video%5C%22%3Eschools%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20everywhere%20with%20Muslims.%20Hindus%20well%20versed%20in%20modern%20technologies%20use%20social%20media%20to%20abuse%20Muslims%20in%20the%20most%20creative%20and%20vilest%20forms.%20Everyone%20knows%20that%20it%20is%20difficult%20for%20Muslims%20to%20respond%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20verbal%20abuses%20that%20a%20BJP%20MP%20unleashed%20at%20a%20Muslim%20MP%20are%20ones%20that%20Hindu%20society%20cannot%20run%20away%20from.%20These%20are%20the%20same%20words%20that%20are%20now%20recited%20in%20the%20form%20of%20songs%2C%20slogans%2C%20and%20as%20chants%20on%20many%20festivals%20to%20give%20sacred%20joy%20to%20sections%20of%20Hindus.%20There%20is%20no%20evidence%20that%20Hindus%20have%20objected%20to%20or%20stopped%20such%20verbal%20abuses%20being%20aired%20on%20loudspeakers.%20More%20and%20more%20are%20now%20becoming%20devotees%20of%20such%20%E2%80%98Babas%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Sadhavis%E2%80%99%20whose%20sermons%20are%20nothing%20but%20a%20torrent%20of%20abuses%20against%20Muslims%2C%20to%20incite%20violence%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fsadhvi-vibhanands-call-to-rape-muslim-women-with-impunity-shows-hindutvas-politics-of-fear%5C%22%3ESadhvi%20Vibhanand%E2%80%99s%20Call%20to%20%E2%80%98Rape%E2%80%99%20Muslim%20Women%20With%20Impunity%20Shows%20Hindutva%E2%80%99s%20Politics%20of%20Fear%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20difficult%20to%20understand%20the%20humiliation%20of%20being%20forced%20to%20remain%20silent%20after%20being%20subjected%20to%20such%20abuses%2C%20repeatedly.%20When%20a%20whole%20community%20is%20compelled%20to%20bear%20with%20it%2C%20what%20does%20it%20mean%20for%20the%20self%20image%20of%20that%20community%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBy%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CThese%20abuses%20are%20not%20new%2C%20Muslims%20hear%20them%20everyday%20from%20the%20mouths%20of%20ordinary%20Hindus%2C%20so%20why%20are%20you%20so%20shocked%3F%E2%80%9D%20we%20are%20undermining%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20crime%20that%20the%20BJP%20MP%20has%20committed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20being%20said%20that%20the%20privilege%20of%20the%20MPs%20can%20be%20used%20to%20platform%20anti-Muslim%20slurs.%20The%20parliament%20can%20be%20made%20a%20place%20to%20humiliate%20Muslims.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthe-sengol-a-spectacle-of-sovereignty-for-new-india%5C%22%3Efull%20meaning%20of%20the%20Sengol%20installation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20symbol%20of%20Hindu%20power%20in%20the%20parliament%2C%20could%20be%20revealed%20only%20by%20the%20anti-Muslim%20slurs%20of%20the%20BJP%20MP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20exposes%20the%20reality%20of%20the%20abuser%2C%20his%20claim%20to%20be%20civilised.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20BJP%20you%20need%20to%20be%20crude%20and%20foul%20if%20you%20want%20to%20rise.%20This%20is%20proved%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20all%20leaders%20joining%20it%20are%20competing%20with%20each%20other%20%E2%80%93%20and%20established%20foul%20mouths%20like%20Modi%20and%20Adityanath%20%E2%80%93%20to%20prove%20that%20they%20are%20no%20less.%20They%20have%20to%20prove%20that%20they%20are%C2%A0%20%C2%A0worthy%20of%20being%20considered%20as%20BJP%20leaders%20by%20humiliating%20the%20opposition%20or%20the%20Muslims.%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20is%20an%20example%20of%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20not%20do%20to%20lament%2C%20it%20is%20futile%20to%20ask%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20PM%20to%20draw%20a%20line%20as%20they%20have%20always%20been%20legitimisers%20and%20enablers%20of%20this%20anti-Muslim%20hatred.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695546360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F24142954%2FScreenshot-2023-09-24-at-2.29.47-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Framesh-bhiduri-anti-muslim-narendra-modi-danish-ali%22%2C%22summary%22%