mesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fbollywood-trivia-do-you-know-parineeti-chopra-is-a-big-fan-of-saif-ali-khan%2Farticleshow%2F103886287.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Employees%20of%20PSU%20Which%20Makes%20Equipment%20for%20ISRO%20Haven't%20Received%20Salaries%20for%20Nearly%202%20Years%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F24135147%2Fpghd01b.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20employees%20of%20Heavy%20Engineering%20Corporation%20(HEC)%2C%20who%20make%20equipment%20for%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%2C%20have%20not%20received%20their%20salaries%20for%20almost%20two%20years%20now.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fengineers-who-built-chandrayaan-3-launch-pad-await-pay-since-20-months%2Farticle67331950.ece%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%203%2C000-strong%20workforce%20of%20the%20public%20sector%20undertaking%20are%20now%20forced%20to%20%E2%80%9Cto%20sell%20edibles%20and%20garments%E2%80%9D%20as%20they%20have%20to%20engage%20as%20part-time%20daily%20wage%20workers%2C%20including%20driving%20autorickshaws%20because%20they%20have%20not%20been%20paid%20their%20rightful%20salaries%20for%20the%20last%2020%20months.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeveral%20other%20news%20organisations%20have%20been%20reporting%20about%20it%20for%20some%20time%20now.%20According%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fno-salary-for-18-months-heavy-engineering-corporation-staff-to-protest-in-delhi-with-cut-out-replicas-of-chandrayaan-3%2Fcid%2F1967481%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20over%20100%20employees%20of%20the%20PSU%20also%20protested%20with%20a%20replica%20of%20Chandrayaan-3%20at%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Jantar%20Mantar%20to%20demand%20payment%20of%20their%20salaries.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHEC%20Majdoor%20Union%20president%20Bhawan%20Singh%20had%20told%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20September%2020%20that%20several%20Lok%20Sabha%20members%20had%20stood%20in%20solidarity%20with%20the%20Union%E2%80%99s%20cause.%20Its%20members%20were%20also%20trying%20to%20meet%20the%20Union%20heavy%20industries%20minister%20Mahendranath%20Pandey.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20this%20was%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20they%20were%20seeking%20an%20audience%20with%20the%20minister%20concerned.%20Interestingly%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Franchi%2Funion-min-assures-help-to-protesting-hec-employees%2Farticleshow%2F97752684.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20reported%20in%20February%20this%20year%20that%20the%20minister%20had%20assured%20the%20Union%20of%20taking%20concrete%20steps%20to%20disburse%20the%20salaries%20of%20the%20HEC%20employees.%20But%2C%20in%20the%20month%20of%20September%2C%20the%20employees%20are%20back%20to%20protesting%20again%20since%20the%20minister%E2%80%99s%20promise%20did%20not%20materialise.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fhindi%2Farticles%2Fcyxdyxdqex5o%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBBC%20Hindi%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Ehas%20reported%20that%20the%20HEC%20has%20made%20several%20important%20equipment%20for%20ISRO%2C%20including%20the%20mobile%20launching%20pedestal%2C%20along%20with%20a%20hammerhead%20tower%20crane%2C%20a%20EOT%20crane%2C%20a%20folding-cum-vertical%20repositionable%20platform%20and%20horizontal%20sliding%20doors.%20The%20report%20clarified%20that%20the%20PSU%20did%20not%20make%20any%20machines%20for%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20mission%20that%20was%20launched%20recently.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBBC%20Hindi%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Equoted%20a%20manager%20at%20HEC%2C%20Purendu%20Dutt%20Mishra%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CTechnically%20the%20government%20would%20be%20correct%20to%20say%20that%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20make%20any%20specific%20equipment%20for%20Chandrayaan-3.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20no%20other%20company%20in%20India%20makes%20such%20launchpads%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20no%20salaries%2C%20employees%20have%20been%20finding%20it%20extremely%20difficult%20to%20support%20their%20families%2C%20the%20report%20notes.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBBC%20Hindi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20quoted%20an%20employee%2C%20Deepak%20Uparia%2C%20as%20saying%20that%20when%20he%20found%20that%20making%20the%20ends%20meet%20had%20become%20completely%20impossible%2C%20Deepak%20and%20his%20wife%20started%20selling%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eidlis%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20the%20street.%20Maslan%20Madhur%20Kumar%20is%20selling%20momos%2C%20while%20Prasanna%20Bhoi%20has%20opened%20a%20tea-shop.%20Deepak%20has%20also%20mortgaged%20the%20jewellery%20of%20his%20wife.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20many%20employees%20have%20withdrawn%20their%20provident%20funds%20too%20while%20some%20have%20taken%20loans%20from%20friends%20and%20relatives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EQuoting%20a%20reply%20given%20in%20parliament%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20in%20August%202023%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBBC%20Hindi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20reported%20that%20since%20the%20HEC%20is%20a%20registered%20and%20an%20independent%20entity%2C%20it%20is%20supposed%20to%20raise%20funds%20for%20its%20operations%20on%20its%20own.%20However%2C%20as%20per%20the%20reply%2C%20the%20organisation%20has%20been%20incurring%20losses%20for%20the%20past%20five%20years.%20In%202023%2C%20its%20loss%20amount%20reached%20Rs%20283.58%20crore.%20The%20absence%20of%20modern%20equipment%20and%20full-time%20leadership%20has%20been%20listed%20as%20main%20reasons%20for%20the%20company%20performing%20poorly%2C%20as%20far%20as%20the%20financials%20are%20concerned%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBBC-Hindi%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%20in%20its%20detailed%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Epiece%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695543812000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F24135147%2Fpghd01b.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Femployees-of-psu-which-makes-equipment-for-isro-havent-received-salaries-for-2-years%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Union%20minister%20had%20assured%20the%20PSU%20union%20that%20salaries%20would%20be%20disbursed%20in%20February%20this%20year.%20However%2C%20so%20salaries%20were%20paid%20and%20employees%20are%20back%20to%20protesting%20in%20Jharkhand%20and%20Delhi.%C2%A0%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A39%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Femployees-of-psu-which-makes-equipment-for-isro-havent-received-salaries-for-2-years%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22All%20you%20need%20to%20know%20about%20Hellbound%20S2%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695543076000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103905520%2Cimgsize-87196.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fkorean%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-hellbound-season-2-cast-updates-release-speculations-and-more%2Farticleshow%2F103905525.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22