%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F23174531%2Fimage-1350.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20Teachers%E2%80%99%20Association%20(JNUTA)%20on%20Friday%2C%20September%2022%20raised%20concerns%20over%20the%20deteriorating%20condition%20of%20the%20university%2C%20including%C2%A0academic%20standards%2C%20rule%20violations%2C%20admission%20issues%2C%20and%20reduced%20diversity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20released%20a%20report%2C%20titled%20%E2%80%98JNU%3A%20The%20State%20of%20the%20University%E2%80%99%20report%2C%20highlighting%20a%20series%20of%20critical%20issues%20affecting%20the%20university%2C%20spanning%20from%20governance%20concerns%20to%20academic%20irregularities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20JNUTA%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6the%20process%20of%20destruction%20of%20the%20university%20unleashed%20from%202016%20has%20continued%20abated%2C%20even%20after%20the%20change%20of%20the%20Vice%20Chancellor%20in%20February%202022.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20destruction%20involves%20erosion%20of%20the%20institutional%20and%20academic%20ethos%20of%20the%20University%20and%20the%20undermining%20of%20its%20role%20as%20a%20promoter%20of%20social%20equity%20%E2%80%93%20the%20hallmarks%20of%20the%20University%20which%20were%20integral%20to%20establishing%20it%20as%20a%20premier%20higher%20education%20institution%2C%E2%80%9D%20read%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F23174838%2Fimage-1351.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F23174838%2Fimage-1351.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F23174838%2Fimage-1351-300x169.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F23174838%2Fimage-1351-1024x578.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-674515%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22677%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPosters%20displayed%20at%20the%20JNUTA%20office%2C%20highlighting%20the%20issues%20mentioned%20in%20%E2%80%98JNU%3A%20The%20State%20of%20the%20University%E2%80%99%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EJNUTA%20president%20D.K.%20Lobiyal%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20happened%20after%20Santishree%20Pandit%20%5Bthe%20current%20Vice%20Chancellor%5D%20joined%20JNU%20in%202022%3F%20We%20had%20thought%20that%20there%20would%20be%20some%20substantial%20change%2C%20but%20nothing%20happened.%20%5BNothing%20changed%20in%5D%20the%20way%20appointments%20are%20made%2C%20recruitment%20is%20done.%20And%20people%20are%20waiting%20for%20the%20last%20seven%20to%2010%20years%20for%20their%20promotions.%20And%20promotions%20are%20very%20selectively%20done.%20So%2C%20people%20are%20waiting%2C%20and%20this%20is%20one%20part%20of%20the%20report.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20alleges%20that%20teachers%20are%20subjected%20to%20harassment%20for%20any%20matter%20they%20choose%20to%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLeave%20for%20academic%20purposes%20is%20a%20facility%20granted%20to%20teachers%20for%20their%20academic%20improvements%20and%20achievements%2C%20which%20ultimately%20benefit%20the%20institutions%20of%20higher%20learning.%20Unless%20there%20is%20any%20specific%20exigency%2C%20any%20leave%20that%20a%20faculty%20member%20is%20eligible%20for%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20granted%20as%20a%20matter%20of%20routine%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20restrictions%20have%20been%20imposed%20on%20such%20leaves%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJNU%20professor%20Surjit%20Mujumdar%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20asking%20for%20a%20leave%20amounts%20to%20harassment.%3Cstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20process%20of%20granting%20leave%2C%20the%20process%20of%20promotions%2C%20or%20any%20such%20case%2C%20any%20matter%20that%20teachers%20have%20to%20take%20up%2C%20they%20are%20subjected%20to%20all%20kinds%20of%20harassment%20and%20victimization.%20No%20one%20knows%20where%20the%20file%20is%2C%20where%20the%20application%20is%20going.%20People%20have%20to%20run%20up%20and%20down%20the%20administrative%20offices%20and%20spend%20long%20periods%20of%20time%20in%20that%20particular%20process.%20The%20administration%20has%20built%20this%20kind%20of%20insensitivity%2C%20where%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20accountability%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETeachers%20attribute%20the%20reasons%20for%20such%20an%20appalling%20condition%20to%20bureaucratization%20and%20administrative%20apathy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fdocument%2F673102717%2FJNU-State-of-the-University-Report%23from_embed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22View%20JNU%20State%20of%20the%20University%20Report%20on%20Scribd%5C%22%3EJNU%20State%20of%20the%20University%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fuser%2F524756983%2FTaniya-Roy%23from_embed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22View%20Taniya%20Roy's%20profile%20on%20Scribd%5C%22%3ETaniya%20Roy%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Scribd%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fembeds%2F673102717%2Fcontent%3Fstart_page%3D1%26view_mode%3Dscroll%26access_key%3Dkey-X1fNYrG6Sbi0ZsikPitu%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20data-auto-height%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20data-aspect-ratio%3D%5C%220.7074509803921568%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22JNU%20State%20of%20the%20University%20Report%20%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20introduction%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98leave%20committee%E2%80%99%20without%20statutory%20backing%20has%20hindered%20the%20academic%20leave%20processes%2C%20resulting%20in%20unreasonable%20demands%20and%20delays.%20Additionally%2C%2048%20teachers%20were%20issued%20charge-sheets%2C%20alleging%20they%20participated%20in%20%E2%80%98illegal%E2%80%99%20protests%2C%20noted%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETheir%20pensionary%20benefits%20were%20withheld%20until%20court%20orders%20intervened%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20retiring%20teachers%20are%20denied%20recognition%20for%20their%20contributions%20through%20honorary%20appointments%20as%20Emeritus%20Professors%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERecent%20years%20have%20witnessed%20substantial%20changes%20in%20the%20JNU%20governance.%20These%20changes%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report%2C%20have%20had%20far-reaching%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20important%20concerns%20is%20the%20abandonment%20of%20the%20seniority-based%20rotation%20system%20for%20appointing%20chairpersons%20and%20deans%20%E2%80%93%20a%20practice%20that%20has%20eroded%20collegial%20decision-making%20structures%20and%20faculty%20representation%20in%20key%20statutory%20bodies%20like%20the%20academic%20and%20executive%20Councils.%20And%20this%20practice%20persists%20in%20defiance%20of%20court%20orders%20and%20regulations%2C%20noted%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20the%20transition%20to%20online%20meetings%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20has%20raised%20questions%20about%20transparency%20and%20meaningful%20discussions%2C%20as%20agenda-driven%20items%20are%20swiftly%20approved%2C%20often%20omitting%20crucial%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeetings%20often%20fail%20to%20meet%20regulatory%20standards%2C%20as%20many%20emergency%20meetings%20happen%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20formality.%20These%20problems%20highlight%20the%20difficulties%20in%20maintaining%20institutional%20autonomy%20and%20governance%20at%20the%20university%2C%20alleged%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20during%20the%20previous%20administration%2C%20faculty%20promotions%20at%20the%20university%20were%20contentious%2C%20often%20tied%20to%20compliance%20with%20the%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20mentioned%20that%20after%20the%20leadership%20changed%20in%20February%202022%2C%20a%20JNUTA%20study%20had%20revealed%20that%20276%20faculty%20members%2C%20primarily%20assistant%20and%20associate%20professors%2C%20were%20eligible%20for%20promotions.%20However%2C%20a%20staggering%2076.4%25%20of%20them%20had%20been%20waiting%20for%20promotions%20for%20over%20four%20years.%20Further%2C%2062%25%20had%20reached%20the%20stage%20where%20even%20their%20next%20promotion%20had%20become%20due.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20promotion%20processes%20have%20resumed%2C%20progress%20is%20slow%2C%20and%20the%20reasons%20for%20delays%20remain%20unresolved.%20In%20four%20regular%20meetings%2C%20the%20executive%20council%20considered%2091%20promotion%20cases%2C%20with%20only%20one%20rejection%2C%20but%20the%20number%20of%20promotions%20processed%20remains%20fewer%20than%20the%20pending%20cases%2C%20said%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695472116000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F23174531%2Fimage-1350.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fjnu-teachers-association-raises-concerns-over-academic-standards-harassment-governance-issues%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20new%20report%2C%20JNUTA%20highlighted%20several%20critical%20issues%20impacting%20the%20university.%20Teachers%20attribute%20the%20root%20causes%20of%20this%20deplorable%20condition%20to%20bureaucratization%20and%20administrative%20apathy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A51%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fjnu-teachers-association-raises-concerns-over-academic-standards-harassment-governance-issues%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22New%20paths%