tion%20for%20school%20students%20to%20supplement%20my%20income.%20I%20used%20to%20tutor%20from%206%20am%20to%2010%20am%2C%20then%20attend%20school%20until%204%20pm%2C%20and%20return%20to%20tutor%20again%20until%206%20pm.%20That%E2%80%99s%20how%20I%20managed%20for%20the%20first%20six%20years%20in%20private%20service%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20the%20teacher.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20also%20the%20time%20when%20Nagaland%20was%20facing%20insurgency%20issues.%20But%20the%20teacher%20didn%E2%80%99t%20let%20that%20hinder%20his%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%201996%2C%20Nellayapan%20got%20a%20job%20as%20a%20postgraduate%20teacher%20in%20physics%20at%20the%20Government%20Higher%20Secondary%20School%20in%20Dimapur.%20In%201999%2C%20he%20got%20married%20and%20remembers%20how%20they%20then%20put%20an%20asbestos%20roof%20on%20their%20house.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20burden%20of%20responsibility%20is%20often%20a%20blessing.%20I%20had%20to%20move%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20he%20went%20on%20to%20become%20the%20school%20principal%20in%202012%20and%20continued%20working%20there%20till%202017.%20Then%2C%20in%202018%2C%20he%20was%20appointed%20as%20the%20assistant%20director%20at%20the%20Directorate%20of%20School%20Education%20in%20Nagaland%2C%20and%20in%202022%2C%20he%20was%20promoted%20to%20the%20role%20of%20deputy%20director.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20trailblazer%20in%20education%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20640px)%20100vw%2C%20640px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnellayapan-family-1695049875.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nellayapan%20B's%20family%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnellayapan-family-1695049875.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnellayapan-f