most%20of%20her%20childhood%2C%20she%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20traditional%20Kottayam-styled%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELaced%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F314288%2Fkochi-architect-koshy-builds-office-with-discarded-mangalore-tiles-repurposed-wood-steel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMangalore%20tiles%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20traditional%20architecture%2C%20the%20house%2C%20as%20per%20Anupa%2C%20%E2%80%9Chas%20a%20soul%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20kept%20intact.%E2%80%9D%20So%20when%20the%20time%20to%20renovate%20the%20100-year-old%20residence%20came%2C%20Anupa%2C%20an%20architect%20and%20designer%2C%20knew%20where%20to%20look%20for%20inspiration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20knew%20I%20was%20not%20going%20to%20bring%20it%20down%20and%20make%20it%20modern%20but%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F247372%2Fkerala-ecofriendly-sustainable-low-cost-home-ashokan-padapelly-fisherman-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20incorporate%20modern%20amenities%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewhile%20keeping%20the%20authenticity%20of%20the%20house.%20I%20did%20not%20have%20to%20look%20anywhere%20for%20inspiration%2C%20the%20bones%20and%20structure%20of%20the%20house%20were%20inspiration%20enough%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20step%20into%20the%20house%20today%2C%20everything%20around%20you%20changes.%20It%20isn%E2%80%99t%202023%20anymore%2C%20but%20you%20are%20transported%20back%20to%20the%20early%201900s.%20Everything%20from%20the%20flooring%20and%20the%20house%E2%80%99s%20layout%20to%20the%20furniture%20gives%20a%20glimpse%20of%20the%20bygone%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EModernising%20the%20house%20while%20preserving%20its%20authenticity%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20Kottayam%2C%20Kerala%2C%20the%203