intact.%20I%20added%20a%20few%20more%20windows%20to%20utilise%20the%20sun%20to%20the%20fullest%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20also%20has%20a%20very%20strong%20foundation%20with%20mortar%20bricks.%20I%20did%20not%20want%20to%20touch%20them%20as%20they%20were%20the%20foundation%20of%20the%20building%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhenever%20I%20saw%20the%20house%2C%20I%20always%20thought%20about%20how%20many%20man-hours%20must%20have%20gone%20into%20making%20it%20100%20years%20ago.%20The%20skill%20and%20masonry%20must%20be%20preserved%2C%20and%20therefore%2C%20when%20I%20decided%20to%20pull%20down%20the%20garage%2C%20I%20used%20manual%20labour%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Anupa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-2-1694786653.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20house%20has%20several%20windows%20to%20utilise%20the%20wind%20and%20keep%20the%20house%20cool%20naturally.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-2-1694786653.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-2-1694786653-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-2-1694786653-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-2-1694786653-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-2-1694786653-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330102%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20house%20has%20several%20windows%20to%20utilise%20the%20wind%20and%20keep%20the%20house%20cool%20naturally.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Anupa%20Kurian%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20would%20have%20taken%20a%20JCB%20just%20minutes%20to%20break%20the%20place%20down%2C%20but%20all%20the%20bricks%20would%20have%20gone%20to%20waste.%20Because%20of%20using%20manual%20labour%20instead%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20use%20those%20bricks%20in%20constructing%20some%20of%20the%20extensions%20in%20my%20room%20and%20the%20patio%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20my%20father%20was%20against%20removing%20the%20garage%20and%20constructing%20a%20patio%2C%20presently%20he%20is%20the%20one%20who%20uses%20it%20the%20most!%E2%80%9D%20she%20laughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20example%20where%20Anupa%20chose%20to%20keep%20the%20originality%20of%20the%20house%20is%20with%20the%20roof%20rafters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20house%20was%20built%20using%20wooden%20rafters%20and%20most%20of%20the%20people%20advised%20us%20to%20change%20it%20to%20steel.%20However%2C%20on%20inspection%2C%20I%20found%20that%20the%20roof%20was%20stronger%20than%20ever.%20I%20decided%20to%20go%20against%20all%20that%20advice%20and%20kept%20the%20original%20rafters%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20Today%2C%20the%20wooden%20rafters%20give%20the%20house%20a%20rustic%20and%20more%20traditional%20look.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EChampioning%20sustainability%20during%20renovation%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnuja%20further%20shares%20that%20to%20keep%20the%20house%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F318502%2Fgujarat-eco-friendly-home-stays-cool-without-air-conditioners-sustainable-architecture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20cool%20during%20harsh%20summers%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20she%20made%20two%20water%20bodies%20on%20the%20northern%20side%20of%20the%20house%20to%20help%20cool%20the%20wind%20that%20enters%20her%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20the%20house%20more%20sustainable%2C%20Anupa%20also%20added%20water%20gutters%20on%20the%20roof%20to%20use%20the%20rainwater.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20water%20from%20the%20gutters%20flows%20into%20the%20two%20ponds%20that%20we%20have%2C%20and%20we%20also%20store%20it%20to%20use%20the%20water%20for%20landscaping%20the%20house.%20Although%20my%20parents%20did%20not%20understand%20the%20need%20for%20the%20gutters%2C%20I%20wanted%20the%20house%20to%20be%20as%20sustainable%20as%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-3-1694786857.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Anupa%20was%20able%20to%20renovate%20the%20house%20fully%20for%20just%20Rs%2030%20lakh.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-3-1694786857.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-3-1694786857-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-3-1694786857-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-3-1694786857-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-3-1694786857-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330104%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAnupa%20was%20able%20to%20renovate%20the%20house%20fully%20for%20Rs%2030%20lakh.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Anupa%20Kurian%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20encountering%20some%20opposition%20due%20to%20its%20divergence%20from%20current%20trends%2C%20she%20has%20chosen%20to%20preserve%20the%20original%20mosaic%20floors%20of%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20looked%20old%20and%20was%20losing%20its%20charm.%20Most%20of%20my%20family%20and%20friends%20suggested%20that%20we%20change%20it%20but%20I%20wanted%20to%20preserve%20it.%20I%20got%20it%20polished%20and%20renewed.%20We%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20feedback%20from%20my%20friends%20and%20family%20later%2C%20and%20most%20of%20them%20loved%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRevival%20of%20old%20materials%20is%20something%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20with%20this%20house.%20We%20have%20used%20a%20lot%20of%20old%20furniture%20lying%20in%20the%20garage%20to%20make%20new%20furniture.%20My%20bed%2C%20for%20instance.%20Also%2C%20the%20new%20windows%20were%20made%20using%20the%20wood%20from%20the%20old%20windows%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20substances%20used%20in%20the%20renovation%20of%20the%20house%20are%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F328878%2Fcouple-builds-saroga-woods-carbon-friendly-solar-powered-sustainable-homestay-in-himachal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecycled%20and%20upcycled%20materials.%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9CUpcycling%20and%20recycling%20the%20materials%20while%20refurbishing%20the%20house%20helped%20us%20save%20a%20lot%20of%20money.%20Most%20of%20our%20family%20and%20friends%20speculated%20the%20cost%20to%20be%20around%20Rs%2070%20lakh%20when%20we%20started%20and%20advised%20us%20to%20construct%20a%20new%20house%20instead.%20However%2C%20I%20told%20them%20I%20will%20bring%20down%20the%20cost%20simply%20by%20reusing%20things%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%20is%20precisely%20what%20Anupa%20did%2C%20and%20she%20was%20able%20to%20renovate%20the%20house%20fully%20for%20just%20Rs%2030%20lakh%2C%20she%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCp-DrilPmyl%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2